description: Terrific - 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo with large living room, including fireplace and high ceilings providing volume.  Each bedroom has walk in closets (California style). The kitchen is modern and offers countertop seating.  The fireplace - is gas and provides both warmth as well as a warm ambiance. There is also a small deck - for outside activities, such as electric grilling or just relaxing outside. The building is professionally managed - with a very low HOA.  Each of the 9 units HAS A DEDICATED PARKING SPOT IN THE ATTACHED GARRAGE IN BUILDING.  In addition, this unit has one very large storage unit in the basement - large enough to house kayaks, bikes etc.  The access to the T - subway station, as well as 93 and Mass Pike are likely 2nd to no other location.  South Boston has emerged as a heaven for many different restaurants, and entertainment.  In addition, the bay and ocean are very close for additional recreation.
